window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Dhruv has been working hard to get investors for his dream venture to save it from collapsing. Shanaya is by his side through thick and thin and stands as a strong pillar of support. Little does the boss know that she has had a crush on him for years, ever since college to be precise. </p> <p>With women drooling over Dhruv and multiple offers distracting him, will the hot and charming Shanaya ever be able to confess her love for him? As the situation gets hard, the hot gets going. Fate finally gives her a chance to work her magic on board a flight, 40,000 feet up in the air. </p> <p>Will she finally win him over when things get <i>Wet at 40,000 Feet</i>?</p>"; 
